# ELIZA CHATBOT

# Overview

This project is a simple implementation of the ELIZA chatbot, created using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. The chatbot runs entirely on client side, with no external libraris or APIs, and is deployed using GitHub Pages.
[View the Chatbot on GitHub Pages]()

# Table of Contents


# Running the project

Running locally:

clone the repository to your local machine:
git clone https://github.com/nelsondca/Emerging-Technologies.git
navigate to the project directory
Open index.html in your web browser to start chatbot

# Github Pages Deployment

This project uses GitHub Actions to deploy to GitHub Pages automatically. Every time you push to the main branch, the workflow will build and deploy the eliza directory to GitHub Pages.

GitHub Actions and Workflow (.github/worfklows/deploy.yml)



